customMethods.script:
import time
	
	# Rotate icon 360 degrees.
	for degree in range(0,361, 10):
		self.props.style.transform = 'rotate(' + str(degree) + 'deg)'
		time.sleep(0.0278)

config.script:
selectedRowData = self.view.custom.RowData
	selectedScheduleID = selectedRowData[0]["ID"]
	selectedWorkOrderID = selectedRowData[0]["WorkOrderID"]
	selectedWorkOrderData = []
	existingQuantity = selectedRowData[0]["Quantity"]
	existingLineID = selectedRowData[0]["LineID"]
	
	for workOrder in self.view.custom.WorkOrderData:
		if workOrder["ID"] == selectedWorkOrderID:
			selectedWorkOrderData.append(workOrder)
	
	modalName = "editSchedule"
	modalPath = "App/Schedule/ScheduleManagement/Embedded/Popups/ScheduleWO"
	
	params = {
		"ModalName": modalName,
		"RowData": selectedWorkOrderData,
		"ScheduledID": selectedScheduleID,
		"IsEdit": True,
		"ExistingQuantity": existingQuantity,
		"ExistingLineID": existingLineID
	}
	
	errorParams = {
		"ModalName": "ErrorModal",
		"ErrorMessage": "Please select a row first!"
	}
	
	if len(selectedRowData) > 0:
		system.perspective.openPopup(modalName, modalPath, params, title="Edit Schedule", modal=True, overlayDismiss=True)
	else:
		system.perspective.openPopup("ErrorModal", "GlobalComponents/Modals/ErrorModal", errorParams)

selectedRowData = self.view.custom.RowData
		
	modalName = "editSchedule"
	modalPath = "App/Schedule/ScheduleManagement/Embedded/Popups/EditScheduleItem"
	
	params = { "RowData": selectedRowData, "ModalName": modalName }
	
	errorParams = {
		"ModalName": "ErrorModal",
		"ErrorMessage": "Please select a row first!"
	}
	
	if len(selectedRowData) > 0:
		system.perspective.openPopup(
			modalName, 
			modalPath, 
			params, 
			title="Edit Schedule", 
			modal=True, 
			overlayDismiss=True)
	else:
		system.perspective.openPopup("ErrorModal", 
		"GlobalComponents/Modals/ErrorModal", 
		errorParams)
